<http://spdx.org/licenses/blessing> <http://spdx.org/rdf/terms#standardLicenseTemplate> "The author disclaims copyright to this source code. In place of a legal notice, here is a blessing:\n\n   May you do good and not evil.\n\n   May you find forgiveness for yourself and forgive others.\n\n   May you share freely, never taking more than you give.\n   \n   " .
