<http://spdx.org/licenses/blessing> <http://spdx.org/rdf/terms#licenseTextHtml> "\n        <p>The author disclaims copyright to this source code. In place of a legal notice, here is a blessing:</p>\n\n<ul style=\"list-style:none\">\n            \n<li><p>May you do good and not evil.</p>\n</li>\n            \n<li><p>May you find forgiveness for yourself and forgive others.</p>\n</li>\n            \n<li><p>May you share freely, never taking more than you give.</p>\n</li>\n        \n</ul>\n    " .
